Infection Prevention Solutions
Addressing infection control and prevention needs with fully integrated programs that offer a portfolio of products and services, supported by experienced, industry-leading professionals. Our combination of premium hospital-grade products, educational materials and measurement tools and services is a unique offering, providing comprehensive solutions in Hand Hygiene and Skin Care, Surgical Hand Antisepsis and Surface Decontamination that will drive compliance and reduce costs incurred due to healthcare-associated infections.



