Frequently Asked Questions for STERIS PLC (NYSE:STE)
What is STERIS PLC's stock symbol?

STERIS PLC trades on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) under the ticker symbol "STE."



How often does STERIS PLC pay dividends? What is the dividend yield for STERIS PLC?

STERIS PLC declared a quarterly dividend on Tuesday, May 9th. Investors of record on Wednesday, June 7th will be given a dividend of $0.28 per share on Thursday, June 29th. This represents a $1.12 annualized dividend and a dividend yield of 1.37%. The ex-dividend date is Monday, June 5th.  View STERIS PLC's Dividend History.



How were STERIS PLC's earnings last quarter?

STERIS PLC (NYSE:STE) released its quarterly earnings data on Tuesday, May, 9th. The company reported $1.11 earnings per share (EPS) for the quarter, topping analysts' consensus estimates of $1.07 by $0.04. The business earned $681.20 million during the quarter, compared to the consensus estimate of $673.47 million. STERIS PLC had a return on equity of 11.12% and a net margin of 4.20%. The firm's quarterly revenue was down 1.3% on a year-over-year basis. During the same period in the prior year, the firm earned $0.90 EPS.  View STERIS PLC's Earnings History.



When will STERIS PLC make its next earnings announcement?

STERIS PLC is scheduled to release their next quarterly earnings announcement on Tuesday, August, 8th 2017. View Earnings Estimates for STERIS PLC.



What guidance has STERIS PLC issued on next quarter's earnings?

STERIS PLC updated its FY18 earnings guidance on Tuesday, May, 9th. The company provided earnings per share (EPS) guidance of $3.96-4.09 for the period, compared to the Thomson Reuters consensus estimate of $4.08. 



Where is STERIS PLC's stock going? Where will STERIS PLC's stock price be in 2017?

4 brokers have issued 1-year price targets for STERIS PLC's shares. Their forecasts range from $71.00 to $89.00. On average, they anticipate STERIS PLC's share price to reach $80.00 in the next year. View Analyst Ratings for STERIS PLC.



Who are some of STERIS PLC's key competitors?

 Some companies that are related to STERIS PLC include Align Technology (ALGN), Bio-Rad Laboratories (BIO), West Pharmaceutical Services (WST), DexCom (DXCM), Hill-Rom Holdings (HRC), VWR Corporation (VWR), Integra LifeSciences Holdings Corporation (IART), ICU Medical (ICUI), NuVasive (NUVA), LivaNova PLC (LIVN), Nevro Corp. (NVRO), Neogen Corporation (NEOG), Haemonetics Corporation (HAE), Inogen (INGN), Halyard Health (HYH), MiMedx Group (MDXG), CONMED Corporation (CNMD) and Asante Solutions (PUMP).



Who are STERIS PLC's key executives?

STERIS PLC's management team includes the folowing people: Michael J. Tokich, Chief Financial Officer, Senior Vice President, TreasurerKaren Burton, Chief Financial Officer, Chief Accounting Officer, Vice President, ControllerJ. Adam Zangerle, Company SecretaryRichard C. Breeden, DirectorBruce A. Edwards, DirectorCynthia L. Feldmann CPA, DirectorJacqueline B. Kosecoff Ph.D., DirectorDavid Baker Lewis, Director



